	<Title>
		Tendinitis pain: Should I apply ice or heat?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		If tendinitis is recent, ice may be better for reducing pain and inflammation.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Which is better for relieving tendinitis pain &amp;mdash; ice or heat?
	</Question>
